title: Enable Copy/Paste From Emacs -Nw
tags: @zettel _method emacs doomemacs
roam-id: ee596cf6-697c-4be2-952c-c4dc2150aa1c
type: text/markdown

- install `xclip` package to your distribution

- add the following into your `package.el`

  ``` commonlisp
  (package! xclip)
  ```

- sync your doom emacs

- add the following into your `config.el`

  ``` commonlisp
  (use-package! xclip
    :hook (after-init . xclip-mode))
  ```
